name: Ios7-css-ui
tagline: a CSS only iOS7 inspired UI
body:
### Thank you for checking out my iOS7 inspired CSS UI kit.

***

To compile with Sass, run the following command:
`sass --update scss:css`

If you have any questions, feel free to email me at:
[my email address](mailto:apps@roachhd.com)

Happy coding!
KB
